&lt;h3 id="삭제">삭제&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>root@controlplane:~# k delete po webapp
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>pod &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;webapp&amp;#34;&lt;/span> deleted
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="수정">수정&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k edit po redis
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="2-replication-controller">2. Replication Controller&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>What is replica and why need controller?&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>replication controller
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>run multiple instances of a single pod in the k8s cluster&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>특징&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>high availability
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>multiplie pod or single pod&lt;/li>
&lt;li>replication controller ensures that the specified number of pods are running at all times.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Load Balancing &amp;amp; Scaling
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>balance the load&lt;/li>
&lt;li>spans across multiple nodes&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>replication controller
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>old technology&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>replica set
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>recommended&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="생성-1">생성&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># ReplicaSet&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">apps/v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">ReplicaSet&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp-replicaset&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">front-end&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp-pod&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp-pod&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">front-end&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">containers&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">nginx-container&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">nginx&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">replicas&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">selector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">matchLabels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">front-end&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="상태-1">상태&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k get replicasets
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME DESIRED CURRENT READY AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>new-replica-set &lt;span class="m">4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="수정-1">수정&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k edit replicaset
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>replicaset.apps/new-replica-set edited
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>pod 삭제&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k delete po --all
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>자동으로 다시 pod 생성 됨&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>ot@controlplane:~# k get po
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>new-replica-set-7mx8k 0/1 Terminating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 4m22s
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>new-replica-set-7p95n 0/1 ContainerCreating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 17s
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>new-replica-set-dcl5m 0/1 Terminating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 4m22s
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>new-replica-set-hhpm9 0/1 ContainerCreating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 17s
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>new-replica-set-hr54x 0/1 ContainerCreating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 17s
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>new-replica-set-m6dmb 0/1 Terminating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 4m22s
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>new-replica-set-v2vr5 0/1 ContainerCreating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 17s
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>new-replica-set-vmts5 0/1 Terminating &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 4m22s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="scale">scale&lt;/h3>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>replace w\ file&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl replace -f ~~.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>scale w\ file&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl scale --replicas&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">6&lt;/span> -f ~~.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>scale w\ resource&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl scale --replicas&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">6&lt;/span> replicaset myapp-replicaset
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>edit&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl edit replicaset
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>실습&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k scale --replicas&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">5&lt;/span> rs new-replica-set
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>replicaset.apps/new-replica-set scaled
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="3-deployments">3. Deployments&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>rolling updates&lt;/li>
&lt;li>rolling back&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-1.png" alt="img-1">&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="4-namespaces">4. Namespaces&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>user의 실수부터 보호하기 위해서 처음 3개의 namespace가 생성됨
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Default&lt;/li>
&lt;li>kube-system&lt;/li>
&lt;li>kube-public&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>isolate resources between namespace&lt;/li>
&lt;li>own policies
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>each namespace is guaranteed certain amount and does not to use more.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>to reach in same namespace
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>mysql.connect(&amp;quot;db-service&amp;quot;)&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>to reach in other namespace
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>mysql.connect(db-service.dev.svc.cluster.local)&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>{service-name}.{namespace}.{service}-{domain-name}&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="생성-2">생성&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>k create ns dev-ns
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>namespace/dev-ns created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="목록">목록&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k get ns
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>NAME STATUS AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>default Active 88s
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>dev Active 34s
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>finance Active 34s
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>kube-node-lease Active 93s
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>kube-public Active 94s
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>kube-system Active 95s
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>manufacturing Active 33s
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>marketing Active 34s
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>prod Active 33s
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>research Active 33s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="상태-2">상태&lt;/h3>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>--namespace&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl get pods --namespace&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>kube-system
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>-n&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl get pods -n kube-system
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h3 id="change-default">change default&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl config set-context &lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>kubectl config current-context&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span> --namespace&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>dev
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="pod-생성">pod 생성&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>k run redis --image&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>redis --namespace&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>finance
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>pod/redis created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="전체-확인">전체 확인&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>k get po --all-namespaces
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>하나의 값만 찾고 싶을 때&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>k get po --all-namespaces &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> grep -i blue
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="5-services">5. Services&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>allow to communicate w\ people, backend, frontend, extra data source&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>types&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>node port
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>make an internal pod accessible on a port on node&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>cluster ip
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>creates a virtual IP inside the cluster to enable communication b2n different services&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>load balancer
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>provisions a load balancer for service for cloud provider&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>NodePort&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-2.png" alt="img-2">&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>target port&lt;/li>
&lt;li>port
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>port of service itself&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>node port
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>valid range: 30000 ~ 32767&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">SErvice&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">myapp-service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">NodePort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">targetPort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">nodePort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">30008&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>if &lt;code>targetPort&lt;/code> is not given&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>same as &lt;code>port&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>if &lt;code>nodePort&lt;/code> is not given&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>automatically allocated&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>randomly distributed if same port is exists&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>ClusterIP&lt;/strong>
&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-3.png" alt="img-3">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>LoadBalancer&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="상태-3">상태&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k get svc
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>kubernetes ClusterIP 10.96.0.1 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 443/TCP 3m46s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="명령어">명령어&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl expose pod redis --port&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">6379&lt;/span> --name redis-service
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="expose">expose&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl run custom-nginx --image&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>nginx --port&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">8080&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>kubectl run httpd --image&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>httpd:alpine --port&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span> --expose
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="6-imperative-vs-declaritive">6. Imperative vs Declaritive&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-4.png" alt="img-4">&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="infrastructure-as-code">Infrastructure as Code&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-5.png" alt="img-5">&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="kubernetes">Kubernetes&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/cka/core_concepts-6.png" alt="img-6">
&lt;strong>Imperative Commands&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>create objects&lt;/li>
&lt;li>update objects&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>→ hard to keep track&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Imperative Configuration Files&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>create objects
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl create -f ~.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>update obejcts
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl edit ~~ ~~&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl replace -f ~.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Declaritve&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>create objects
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl apply -f ~.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl apply -f /path/to/config-files&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>update objects
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>kubectl apply -f ~.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item></channel></rss>